          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ", but we're guessing that even some of the most diehard 'Vette lovers have never heard of the only Corvette that actually bears Duntov's name. The \"father of the Corvette\" was responsible for helping to make the Corvette an American ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
